[Poland has reported to the OIE a total of 2 ASF outbreaks involving wild boars, both on its border with Belarus. The last follow-up report was submitted on 4 Jul 2014. See the reports and an interactive map at http://www.oie.int/wahis_2/public/wahid.php/Reviewreport/Review/viewsummary?fupser=&dothis=&reportid=15340.

Official confirmation and report on the additional 4 outbreaks is anticipated. - Mod.AS]
